Meet our illustrious jury members for the South Asia Competition.

@pagliji, Head of Jury, an Academy Award-nominated film director known for her groundbreaking films that cross borders of all kinds.

#DavidMichod, Jury Member, is an acclaimed Australian film director, screenwriter, and producer who burst on the scene with 2010’s award-winning crime drama Animal Kingdom. He is associated with a gritty new wave of Australian filmmakers.

@isabelvsandoval, Jury Member: Isabel Sandoval is a director and actress often appreciated for her bold approach to cinematic style and is often described as one of the most exciting and multi-talented filmmakers on the indie scene.

#MarianneKhoury, Jury Member: Marianne Khoury, a prolific producer of award-winning films from Egypt, a film director, and currently the Artistic Director of El Gouna Film Festival

Find more details at www.mumbaifilmfestival.com (link in bio) 

